-- sum-list-crystal.cell: sum a list of numbers

вҠў total
  given values вүЎ [10, 20, 30, 40, 50]
  yield sum-result

  вҲҙ Compute the sum of all numbers in В«valuesВ».

  вҠЁ sum-result = 150

вҠў crystallize
  given В§total
  given totalвҶ’sum-result
  yield В§total', is-faithful

  вҲҙ Read В«В§totalВ». It sums a list.
    Write a вҠў= expression: sum(values)

вҠў verify-crystal
  given В§total'
  given crystallizeвҶ’is-faithful
  given totalвҶ’sum-result
  yield approved

  вҲҙ Does В«В§total'В» produce 150 for [10, 20, 30, 40, 50]?

  вҠЁ if approved and crystallizeвҶ’is-faithful then В§total' may replace В§total
